S'With over 20 million pounds (over 9M kgs) lost by our users, Noom Weight Loss Coach has everything you need to eat well, be active, and stay motivated. Featured in New York Times, Women\'s Health, Shape, Forbes, ABC News!The Coach gives you daily tasks to help create positive lifestyle changes for long-term weight loss. These tasks guide you through a scientifically-backed weight loss plan that provides informational articles, fun challenges, a daily Noom score to track how you\xe2\x80\x99re doing, activity reminders, plus easy and convenient food and exercise logging \xe2\x80\x94 the keys to successful weight loss.Noom Weight Loss Coach features: \xe2\x9c\x93A personalized and interactive weight loss plan that gets you real results and helps keep the pounds off (86% of active users lose weight successfully)\xe2\x9c\x93An easy-to-use, color-coded food logging system that helps you learn what\xe2\x80\x99s healthy and track meals quickly\xe2\x9c\x93An exercise tracker with real-time GPS and pedometer to record all your activities, inside or outside\xe2\x9c\x93Unique daily food and exercise tasks to help get to your goal. You\xe2\x80\x99ll get something new every day to keep your program fresh!\xe2\x9c\x93A single-click logbook to track workouts, meals, and weight loss progress \xe2\x9c\x93Programmable reminders to stay-on-track so you never forget to visit the grocery store or go for that walk or run\xe2\x9c\x93Noom points and levels to reward you and track your progress from day to day\xe2\x9c\x93Tons of helpful and educational articles to give you the scoop on health and wellness\xe2\x9c\x93Motivational home screen widgets to keep you engaged \xe2\x9c\x93User support forums to connect with others, ask questions, and share tips\xe2\x9c\x93Social networking integration with Facebook and Twitter\xe2\x9c\x93Plus many more features and functions updated frequently!-----------What our Noomers have to say:Tracy Great GuidelineLove it! Helps me monitor and be more aware of the food and I am eating, my water intake and keeps me motivated to exercise. Been using it a week so far and have lost 2 pounds!AdrianaLove itHelps me keep everything on track...no other app does it betterStephanie Great!!I love this app! It helps when you can track your eating habits every single day...very helpfulcorboard Its the craZiest thing, but keeping track of how.much "green" I\'ve eaten and seeing my "calories burned" actually makes me want to participate :)suzanne Its been a real eye opener!Its been a real eye opener for me, i never realized before this app how many calories everything you put in your mouth has even if its something small or just a drink, it helping me big time-------------------FAQsQ: Where does nutrition and exercise science for the app come from?A: We have a dedicated team of dieticians, exercise scientists, personal trainers, and behavior experts that program their knowledge into the Noom Weight Loss Coach. Q: What if I already use CardioTrainer or Calorific?A: If you already use CardioTrainer, Noom will NOT erase your data, and you can transfer it using your permanent account. Noom will not share data from CardioTrainer or Calorific, so if you want to record new tracks or food, be sure to do so from Noom.Q: Why does Noom want access to my Google account and contacts? What about other permissions?A: Your Google account is used only to create a permanent account so you can backup and recover your data. The contacts are only used IF you want to connect with friends who also use Noom to track their activity \xe2\x80\x94 it\xe2\x80\x99s not used otherwise. This information is not stored anywhere, nor will it ever be used for any other purpose. More information about the permissions requested by this application: http://goo.gl/lGnJ4Recent changes:3.4.1- Easily edit starting weight from the Weight Loss Plan page- Fixed bug that caused some users\' profile settings to return to default values (e.g. Female, 42 years old)- Lots of stability fixes- Starting weight can go below 99 lbs.- Improved selector spinner in food logging by defaulting to a more appropriate value and spinning faster.'
